        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " … ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "through your faith",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (R. V.). This conveyed the needed solace to the lonely Apostle. Their “faith” was the essential point, that about which Timothy was sent to enquire (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Thessalonians 3:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); if this remained, all would go well. So our Lord prayed for Peter, “That ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "thy faith",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " fail not” (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Luke 22:32",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). “By faith ye stand” (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Corinthians 1:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
